name: Rainbow Tripus (custom by Goto-san)
description:
Rainbow Tripus (custom by Goto-san)
Height = 10 inches

Product Description: Hiroshi Goto-san has been painting Japanese toys and Kaiju for over 40 years in Japan. He's painted for such notable companies as Bandai toys, Takara and Bullmark just to name a few in his long career. Still very much active in the toy painting business he paints for RealXHead, Marusan toys and Max Toy Co. and others. This is a special Kaiju Tripus in his Rainbow style of painting, done on clear vinyl. Don't miss your chance to own one of these hand painted masterpieces by a living legend.
